1. A Boolean value is either true or false. 
3 different expression that results a Boolean type
8 == (12-4)
>> True
5 == (6 + 2)
>> False
1 = "ha"
2 = "noi"
>> 1 + 2 == "hanoi"

2. Flow chart is the chart the shows the steps of a process. 
The steps are represented in boxes which are connected by arrows that shows the 
direction of the steps.

3. Nested conditionals is when we use a conditional inside another conditional.

if x-2 == 0:
    print('x == 2')
else:
    if x-2 < 0:
        print('x < 2')
    if x-2 > 0:
        print('x > 2')
